04-05 December - Almond Cookies

- 2 cup sliced, toasted almonds
- 2     eggs
- 1 cup sugar
- 1 cup light brown sugar
- 1/2   teaspoon cloves
- 2     teaspoon cinnamon
- 1/2   cup oil
- 2     tablespoon water
- 2 1/2 cup flour
- 2     teaspoon baking powder

Mix all ingredients and put onto greased cookie sheets. Baste top of cookies with egg yolks before baking. Preheat oven to 350F and bake for 20-30 minutes. Cut while still warm, place back on cookie sheet and bake another 5 minutes. You could use aluminum trays or loaf pans to get a more uniformed cookie. Bake in an oval shape. After cooled a bit cut into slanted pieces. 